<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA515_04_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema515_04.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2 fraction_title">
        <h2 data-head="2_light_purple" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <div class="mixed_fraction ml_0">
                <span>1</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              +
              <div class="mixed_fraction ml_2">
                <span>2</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>8</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              을 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">자연수는 자연수끼리, 분수는 분수끼리 계산해 보세요.</h3>

            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="container_515">
                <div class="operation_box">
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>4</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1 </span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  = 
                  <div class="pare_wrap">1+2</div>
                  +
                  <div class="pare_wrap">
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                    +
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                =
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="container_515">
                <div class="operation_box">
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>4</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>4</span>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>17</span>
                    <span>8 </span>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <span>8</span>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>17 </span>
                    <span>8</span>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="31"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <span>8</span>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>8</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">분모가 다른 대분수의 덧셈하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p lang="y" lang="y">두 대분수를 통분하여 자연수는 자연수끼리, 분수는 분수끼리 더하거나 대분수를 가분수로 나타내고 두 가분수를 통분하여<br />더합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
